In my golden shoes</p>
<p>It was a wishful dream, but I have to admit<br />
When I woke up, I woke up with pleasure<br />
Me, a singer and dancer<br />
Oh&#8230; oh&#8230;</p>
<p>Diggi-loo diggi-ley, the sky was opening up<br />
You hardly believe your eyes<br />
Oh&#8230; I&#8217;d like to wish<br />
For everyone golden shoes</p>
